{"id": 2441, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心 × vivo NEX】你如何看待智能手机在你生活里扮演的角色？", "description": "来聊聊这个天天陪着你的家伙！（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 10756, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180628192241e1Zp8NEnvkwlRGAP.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-29T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 290048, "content": "伤害情侣的工具t", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805013}, {"id": 290049, "content": "离开手机的时刻，可能就只有考试的那段时间了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387013}, {"id": 290562, "content": "人间没有爱，都是手机害", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390379}, {"id": 290051, "content": "上学想要好手机，毕业后有好手机却发现无趣了，少了什么？少了一起玩耍的朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384239}, {"id": 290563, "content": "坑了眼睛，丰富了思想。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390404}, {"id": 290052, "content": "我希望有一天APP之前可以互联互通，与操作系统完美兼容", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1323352}, {"id": 290053, "content": "变成了我的一个器官～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1308132}, {"id": 290055, "content": "有点害怕。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377273}, {"id": 290056, "content": "越来越傻了，很多东西记不住了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387033}, {"id": 290058, "content": "下一代，手机将奴隶人 。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387036}, {"id": 290059, "content": "合理运用，不能被其所支配！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387039}, {"id": 331532, "content": "认清自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602240}, {"id": 290060, "content": "想离开，但是又离不开", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377387}, {"id": 290061, "content": "指尖毒品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819456}, {"id": 290318, "content": "就像吃饭睡觉一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378907}, {"id": 290063, "content": "当我拿起手机时，心想着:今天又废了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266166}, {"id": 290064, "content": "寡人日日宠幸它 实在做不到与学习雨露均沾啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1180833}, {"id": 290065, "content": "居然成为安全感的来源", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095841}, {"id": 290067, "content": "有它我就会好好利用，没它我也能活的精彩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384646}, {"id": 290068, "content": "我的知心朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327094}, {"id": 290069, "content": "有的时候带我飞翔，有的时候扼住喉咙", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689450}, {"id": 290070, "content": "个人终端，总有一天我们会适应它。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346364}, {"id": 290326, "content": "原来觉得手机好玩，现在连耍手机都变成一件无聊的事了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1388056}, {"id": 293912, "content": "消时片??", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1077676}, {"id": 293913, "content": "绝对离不开?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403791}, {"id": 290074, "content": "单身的原因……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382500}, {"id": 290330, "content": "当自己一个人的时候它是我的好伙伴，身边有人的时候绝不会只顾着低头玩手机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389342}, {"id": 292892, "content": "离不开它呀，主要是手机上联系外部更方便，接收的咨询也更多，现代好青年得与时俱进昂。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403972}, {"id": 290077, "content": "有如伊甸园的那条蛇", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358751}, {"id": 290078, "content": "亲爹", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337451}, {"id": 290079, "content": "越来越焦虑，信息太多，可是已经中毒了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400240}, {"id": 290080, "content": "过马路不长眼的也多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387194}, {"id": 290336, "content": "让我选，我希望回到手机功能局限于电话短信的年代", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020655}, {"id": 291617, "content": "越觉得就像是陪衬  除了必要需要使用  装着不舒服就是拿着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1231418}, {"id": 290082, "content": "让我多了一种依赖病 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182588}, {"id": 290338, "content": "极大提高工作和生活效率和质量", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1385432}, {"id": 290083, "content": "非常出色的工具", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1342980}, {"id": 291619, "content": "工具而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393453}, {"id": 290085, "content": "那是相当重要啊除了吃饭 睡觉 学习 工作 娱乐外的生活必备", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718332}, {"id": 290086, "content": "有不找看到的人时，就特别想丢掉手机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374854}, {"id": 290087, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387271}, {"id": 290088, "content": "伴侣", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324911}, {"id": 290089, "content": "消灭无聊的时光却让人更无聊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133384}, {"id": 293417, "content": "两个月没用手机，发现不用手机挺好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407201}, {"id": 290090, "content": "信息中心\n搜索 阅读 分析 整合", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095949}, {"id": 290346, "content": "工具操控我们，他们越来越智能。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389477}, {"id": 290092, "content": "学习11", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1226022}, {"id": 290348, "content": "阿拉丁神灯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200218}, {"id": 290095, "content": "被监控和引导的魔雾弥漫生活，总有一天要逃跑，拒绝智能机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324544}, {"id": 290096, "content": "离不开了", "image": "img/option/option/201806301101530hdbHwMf3WAtXr5v.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386928}]}